  "texts": [
    "Moreover, creating study resources has been linked to improved comprehension, and retention of content.",
    "When students engage in the process of creating study resources, they must deeply engage with the material, which leads to better internalization and understanding.",
    "This active learning process encourages critical thinking, and allows students to explore the content from different perspectives to reinforce their grasp of the subject matter.",
    "The process of peer assessment is integral to the validation and enhancement of student-created educational resources within the RiPPLE platform.",
    "Upon the creation of resources by students, these materials are subjected to a peer review mechanism whereby peers evaluate the content's quality and relevance."
